<!-- 2012-05-04 RLC
    I created this to describe ratelimiting operations as in http://red.rackspace.com/display/auth/Cloud+Auth+Rate+Limiting. 
    Because this is "an implementation feature not bound to a contract", it's not provided by an extension nor described by a developer-created WADL.
    Because the rest of the API Operations section is constructed from WADLs, 
    if I don't build this the same way it won't be included in things like role="api-reference" summary tables;
    faking up this WADL so ratelimiting operations will match the rest.
    *** I copied this from RAX-KSQA because it is small; taking out its traces from <application> & <grammars>, tho I have no replacements. ***
    *** I have no idea why RAX-KSQA is copyright OpenStack. ***
-->
